column4: Fix some bugs of AI and delete useless code
Fixed a problem with vanishing sub-hyperplanes during BSP tree merging.
some bug fixes  more unit tests
Revert previous commit with debug output  fix typo.
MATH-1198 Simplify FastMath exp function Hopefully also fix Java 1.5 JIT bug
Fix sonar error: remove private final field and return the DEFAULT value instead.

Fixed wrong handling of a corner case.  The problem occurs in very difficult to reproduce cases  as it is really a corner case. When the vanishing cut-subhyperplane occurs during a Difference operation  the fixed node still has a null cut-subhyperplane. This was not proerply handled.  JIRA: MATH-1162

Fixed wrong handling of a corner case.  The problem occurs in very difficult to reproduce cases  as it is really a corner case. When the vanishing cut-subhyperplane occurs during a Difference operation  the fixed node still has a null cut-subhyperplane. This was not properply handled.  JIRA: MATH-1162

Fixed wrong intersection selection in polyhedrons sets.  Sometimes the selected intersection point was on the wrong side of the line (i.e. in the opposite of the direction of the line).  Thanks to Mike Zimmerman for identifying and solving the issue.  JIRA: MATH-1211

Fixed wrong intersection selection in polyhedrons sets.  Sometimes the selected intersection point was on the wrong side of the line (i.e. in the opposite of the direction of the line).  Thanks to Mike Zimmerman for identifying and solving the issue.  JIRA: MATH-1211
Fixed checkstyle and findbugs warnings.
Fixed dummy return that created too much problems.
Fixed error message for unknown parameter name in ODE.  JIRA: MATH-1232
Fixed error message for unknown parameter name in ODE.  JIRA: MATH-1232

Fixed error in computing discrete distribution of D statistics for small-sample 2-sample Kolmogorov-Smirnov tests. Error was causing incorrect p-values returned by exactP and monteCarloP methods (used by default for small  mid-size samples).  JIRA: MATH-1245

Fixed error in computing discrete distribution of D statistics for small-sample 2-sample Kolmogorov-Smirnov tests. Error was causing incorrect p-values returned by exactP and monteCarloP methods (used by default for small  mid-size samples).  JIRA: MATH-1245

Fix compilation problems with java 1.5: remove @Override tags for interfaces  fix problem with cast  remove unneeded type parameters in test methods. Additionally  added @Override tags for implemented abstract methods as suggested by eclipse  small typo fixes.
